testFuzz_parent_correctness_succeeds(uin.notice: Tests that the `parent` function correctly computes the position of the parent.

testFuzz_rightIndex_correctness_succeeds.notice: Tests that the `rightIndex` function correctly computes the deepest, right most index relative         to a given position.

testFuzz_right_correctness_succeeds(uint.notice: Tests that the `right` function correctly computes the position of the right child.

testFuzz_traceAncestor_correctness_succe.notice: Tests that the `traceAncestor` function correctly computes the position of the         highest ancestor that commits to the same trace index.

test_pos_correctness_succeeds().notice: A static unit test for the correctness of all gindicies, (depth, index) combos,         and the trace index in a tree of max depth = 4.

testFuzz_attack_correctness_succeeds(uin.details: `attack` is an alias for `left`, but we test it separately for completeness.

testFuzz_defend_correctness_succeeds(uin.details: A defense can only be given if the position does not belong to the root claim, hence the bound of [1, 127]      on the depth.
